xwikidoc.content:
This Macros displays data about a GitLab Issue.

Examples

== Display a single Issue in enum mode ==

{{code}}
{{gitlab id="xwiki" projectId="244"}}1{{/gitlab}}
{{/code}}

{{gitlab id="xwiki" projectId="244"}}1{{/gitlab}}

== Display multiples issues in enum mode ==

{{code}}
{{gitlab id="xwiki" projectId="244"}}1,2{{/gitlab}}
{{/code}}

{{gitlab id="xwiki" projectId="244"}}1,2{{/gitlab}}

== Display multiples issues in list mode ==

{{code}}
{{gitlab id="xwiki" projectId="244" style="list"}}1,2{{/gitlab}}
{{/code}}

{{gitlab id="xwiki" projectId="244" style="list"}}1,2{{/gitlab}}

== Display multiples issues in table mode ==

{{code}}
{{gitlab id="xwiki" projectId="244" style="table"}}1,2{{/gitlab}}
{{/code}}

{{gitlab id="xwiki" projectId="244" style="table"}}1,2{{/gitlab}}

== Display multiples issues in report mode ==

{{code}}
{{gitlab id="xwiki" projectId="244" style="report"}}1,2{{/gitlab}}
